sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Main as main()
    participant SA as SpringApplication
    participant SFL as SpringFactoriesLoader
    participant Listeners as RunListeners
    participant Env as Environment
    participant Ctx as ApplicationContext
    participant BF as BeanFactory
    participant Web as WebServer
    participant Runners as Runner

    Main->>SA: new SpringApplication(primarySources)
    activate SA

    SA->>SA: WebApplicationType.deduce()
    Note right of SA: 检测 classpath 判断:<br/>SERVLET / REACTIVE / NONE

    SA->>SFL: 加载 BootstrapRegistryInitializer
    SA->>SFL: 加载 ApplicationContextInitializer
    SA->>SFL: 加载 ApplicationListener
    SA->>SA: deduceMainApplicationClass()

    Main->>SA: run(args)

    SA->>SA: Startup.create() 记录启动时间

    SA->>SA: createBootstrapContext()

    SA->>SFL: 加载 SpringApplicationRunListener
    SFL-->>SA: EventPublishingRunListener

    SA->>Listeners: starting()
    Note right of Listeners: 发布 ApplicationStartingEvent

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over SA,Env: 阶段: 准备 Environment
        SA->>Env: getOrCreateEnvironment()
        SA->>Env: configureEnvironment(args)
        SA->>Env: ConfigurationPropertySources.attach()
        SA->>Listeners: environmentPrepared()
        Note right of Listeners: 发布 ApplicationEnvironmentPreparedEvent<br/>触发加载 application.yml
        SA->>Env: bindToSpringApplication()
    end

    SA->>SA: printBanner()
    Note right of SA: 打印 Spring Boot Banner

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over SA,Ctx: 阶段: 创建 ApplicationContext
        SA->>Ctx: createApplicationContext()
        Note right of Ctx: 根据 WebApplicationType 创建:<br/>AnnotationConfigServletWebServer...<br/>或 AnnotationConfigReactiveWebServer...<br/>或 AnnotationConfigApplicationContext
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over SA,BF: 阶段: 准备 Context
        SA->>Ctx: setEnvironment(env)
        SA->>Ctx: postProcessApplicationContext()
        SA->>SA: applyInitializers(context)
        Note right of SA: 执行所有 ApplicationContextInitializer
        SA->>Listeners: contextPrepared()
        Note right of Listeners: 发布 ApplicationContextInitializedEvent
        SA->>BF: registerSingleton("springApplicationArguments")
        SA->>Ctx: load(sources) 注册主配置类
        SA->>Listeners: contextLoaded()
        Note right of Listeners: 发布 ApplicationPreparedEvent
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over SA,Web: 阶段: 刷新 Context (核心!)
        SA->>Ctx: refresh()
        Note right of Ctx: AbstractApplicationContext.refresh()

        Ctx->>BF: invokeBeanFactoryPostProcessors()
        Note right of BF: 处理 @Configuration<br/>处理 @EnableAutoConfiguration<br/>AutoConfigurationImportSelector 执行<br/>条件评估 + 过滤

        Ctx->>BF: registerBeanPostProcessors()
        Ctx->>BF: finishBeanFactoryInitialization()
        Note right of BF: 创建所有单例 Bean<br/>依赖注入<br/>@PostConstruct 回调

        Ctx->>Web: 创建并启动 WebServer
        Note right of Web: Tomcat/Jetty/Netty<br/>绑定端口<br/>注册 DispatcherServlet

        Ctx->>Ctx: finishRefresh()
        Note right of Ctx: 发布 ContextRefreshedEvent
    end

    SA->>Listeners: started(context)
    Note right of Listeners: 发布 ApplicationStartedEvent

    SA->>Runners: callRunners()
    Note right of Runners: 执行 ApplicationRunner<br/>执行 CommandLineRunner<br/>按 @Order 排序

    SA->>Listeners: ready(context)
    Note right of Listeners: 发布 ApplicationReadyEvent<br/>应用完全就绪!

    deactivate SA

    Note over Main,Web: 应用运行中，等待请求...
